==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Ret
<hw>Ret</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Akin to <ets>rot</ets>.]</ety>
<def>To prepare for use, as flax, by separating the fibers from the
woody part by process of soaking, macerating, and other treatment.</def>
<rj><au>Ure.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Retable</ent>⟦br⟧
